data.description: Check out this beautiful home located at Hedingham on the Neuse!  GOLF COURSE COMMUNITY & BACKS UP TO THE NEUSE RIVER TRAILS!  Fresh paint with an open floor plan!  Many upgrades.  The home is bright and airy!  Kitchen opens to the living room.  The kitchen has granite counters and a breakfast nook with a view to the private fenced backyard.  There is also a shed for extra storage!  This home has hardwood floors and some LPV flooring upstairs.  The owner's retreat is large with WIC and glamour bath!  All other bedrooms are nicely sized with ample closet space for storage.  Irrigation system also included.  GOLF AND ATHLETIC COMMUNITY WITH MANY AMENITIES!!  Pool, work out facilities, etc. Please see photos.  This home is in a convenient location and close to everything!!
